Some of the js or python packages provided (in requirement.txt or packages.json)
by default by the with my installation (python 3.8, node v16.17.1, npm 8.15.0)
raise some issues. So i complete the folling steps:

for the backend uninstall the following:
    pip uninstall python-jose-cryptodome

for the backend install the following:

    pip install certifi
    pip install python-jose[cryptography]

for the frontend uninstall the following:
    npm uninstall node-sass

for the frontend install the following:
    npm install --save-dev sass